THEUNTOUCHABLEONE was bumped at the start by PEDAL TO THE METAL and pinched back, then was allowed to settle in stride, came six-wide into the stretch and gained his best stride too late. BIG GALUTE prompted the issue to the stretch while racing three-wide and weakened. EXIT STAGE LEFT saved ground while racing close up but lacked a rally. PEDAL TO THE METAL broke in and bumped with THEUNTOUCHABLEONE, then was reserved off the pace, came five-wide into the stretch and failed to seriously threaten. POWERS WAR DOG steadied from between horses shortly after the start, then saved ground and failed to menace.
